Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 焦掉了 焦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,专心一点好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水 给我水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰激凌卖完了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 20分钟就卖光啰
