Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比什么V啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是在海边走来走去还晒着太阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差点以为自己要变成木乃伊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活说回来为什么我要当卖冰的小妹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不是为了做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而远道来这平民等级的海边民宿小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了要和花菱少爷一起拥有个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛若Villon所需要的那种夏季禁忌之爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很努力呢 繭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.61,0:03:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是奖励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奖励？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃玩后就开始第二趟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.41,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶 还要去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 很能喝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是有趣的小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯也很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 再来一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 再来两瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要毛豆跟泡菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 你没在帮忙店里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在和老伯试喝来增加营业额啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 老伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚也在这里绊到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心一点比较好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 果然这时候还是该千夏出面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
