Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喝不下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 大哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然年轻但很熟练呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我最喜欢做料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样随时都能做新娘了呢
