Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去洗澡吧 这里让千夏来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？我等一下再去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 请先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多都结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是一身汗味会被大哥哥讨厌的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经有人在洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会是蒂娜学姐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧 妙姐姐
