Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有谁先进来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员？房东小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蒂娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去会被学姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须要想办法瞒混过去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里的是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 蒂娜学姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 是小妙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那边…淋浴不会太热吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 完全没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样 那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我去泡澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好像总算是瞒混过去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学…学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去引开蒂娜学姐她们的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长你就趁机…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷声响彻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔神 吼叫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,击退地球上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是没有品味的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有邪恶 勇气的火焰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 你泡澡能不能安静一点啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学姐 繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？那么慎重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其…其实是…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全长20公尺的萤乌贼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在说什么啊 真是笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样怎么能引开她们的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里 哪里 哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全长20公尺的可是非常大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上当了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在那个是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里？哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是声音是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 是我在拍水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 是不是有动了一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪…哪会可疑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏也可以一起洗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露天澡塘还是要大家一起洗才有趣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家帮彼此洗背好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很好玩的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗吧 洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不好？蒂娜学姐？繭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相洗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 千夏 来洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那身体要先暖一下才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那里不行 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡的时候 浴巾是一定要拿掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千…千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小千千 你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.45,0:10:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放在那边就行了 我会洗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然这个洗碗精很能去除油垢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒啊 好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的我来就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵跟雅就先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两个人不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是泡澡泡过头 不用管它就会好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.53,0:12:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有要搬的东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来就不用了 休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 休息一下后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个地方想请你陪妙子一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有经营摊贩对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然只有周末在卖炒面而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是千夏在做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很能干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有这种老家就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 学…学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.91,0:13:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.05,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前跟千夏两个人摇摇晃晃地搬那个瓦斯桶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确对女孩子来说有点重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说学长厉害嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟我是个男人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害啊 千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用 尝尝味道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去 妙姐姐也吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来 店的准备好了 也还有时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个人去逛逛玩一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管啦 去吧 去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…好像约会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要玩那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一个换妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我好紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像手不听使唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像会失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 要自然一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么 为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.68,0:15:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愈想要表现的自然 身体就愈不听使唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是想到跟学长在一起就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被学长讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟妙子在一起总是会发生意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点都不会无聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.73,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个 你不生气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总是笨手笨脚 老是给学长添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那回事 我很开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子不论遇到什么麻烦 总是会继续努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.41,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…很喜欢那样的妙子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.82,0:17:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长！我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学…学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看到了吗？刚刚的烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没…没听到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 再一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏一定等的不耐烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长 快点 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明就是来玩的却还让你们工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我们很开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还会来的 奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好好 要再来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样？妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大哥哥的感情变得很好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告白了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐大概没办法做到那样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道妙姐姐做了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好狡猾 告诉我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏可是爱的丘比特呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天 跟学长在一起我就了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是现在的我 只会给学长添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要更努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像葵一样能干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像雅一样精明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像蒂娜学姐一样开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.02,0:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也希望能像繭一样坦率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望自己能成为适合学长的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得更加更加努力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明之前就对男生很没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是跟大哥哥在一起时却变得很自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以千夏第一次看到的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就以为他是你男友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.91,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听我说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.89,0:20:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在妙姐姐成为很棒的女人之前
