Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.21,0:20:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？
